```plantuml
@startuml mcuking_offline-package-webpack-plugin
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "Webpack Build Process" as Webpack {
  rectangle "Emit Phase" as Emit #lightsteelblue
}

rectangle "OfflinePackagePlugin" as Plugin #lightyellow {
  rectangle "jszip" as JSZip #aliceblue
  rectangle "mime-types" as MimeTypes #aliceblue
}

rectangle "File System" as FS #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
Developer --> Webpack

' Webpack interactions
Webpack --> Plugin : Initialize with configuration
Emit --> Plugin : Trigger during emit phase

' OfflinePackagePlugin interactions
Plugin --> FS : Read files for zipping
Plugin --> JSZip : Create zip archive
Plugin --> MimeTypes : Detect MIME types
Plugin --> FS : Write index.json\nand zip file

@enduml
```